OL,5,Cforce
OL,7,FThe Water (Special Measures) Act 2025,
OL,8,Fcomes in the face of widespread public
OL,9,Ffury over the degraded state of the
OL,10,Fcountry's rivers, lakes and coastal
OL,11,Fwaters and at a lack of investment in
OL,12,Fwater infrastructure, rising bills,
OL,13,Fhigh dividends and debt and executive
OL,14,Fpay and bonuses.
OL,16,FThe government has also launched an
OL,17,FIndependent Water Commission, which is
OL,18,Flooking at widespread water sector
OL,19,Freform.
