OL,3,CWater bosses could be jailed over
OL,4,Csewage spills as new laws come into
OL,5,Cforce
OL,7,FUntil now, regulators have faced
OL,8,Fobstruction from companies in their
OL,9,Fefforts to gather evidence for
OL,10,Fprosecutions on illegal sewage spills.
OL,12,FDespite obstruction being a criminal
OL,13,Foffence, only three water company
OL,14,Fofficials have been prosecuted by the
OL,15,FEnvironment Agency without appeal, and
OL,16,Fthe maximum punishment was a fine `
OL,17,Falthough no fines were issued.
