OL,3,CWater bosses could be jailed over
OL,4,Csewage spills as new laws come into
OL,5,Cforce
OL,7,FPhilip Duffy, chief executive of the
OL,8,FEnvironment Agency said: "The Water
OL,9,F(Special Measures) Act was a crucial
OL,10,Fstep in making sure water companies
OL,11,Ftake full responsibility for their
OL,12,Fimpact on the environment.
OL,14,F"The tougher powers we have gained
OL,15,Fthrough this legislation will allow
OL,16,Fus, as the regulator, to close the
OL,17,Fjustice gap, deliver swifter
OL,18,Fenforcement action and ultimately
OL,19,Fdeter illegal activity."
